==Religion==

Turkism is the belief in Bob IX, more commonly known as 'Bob the Turkey' or, as many Cowists (worshippers of [[Cowism]]) would call him, 'His Royal Turkey the Creator of Emperor Holy Cow' or more shortly 'His Royal Turkey'. As you may have guessed, this 'Bob the Turkey' is a [[turkey]](animal). Turkists believe that turkeys are very intelligent, and are to be respected. Meimasists take this even further, and are not allowed to harm imprison or even have any contact with a turkey unless it has the turkey's permission to do so.